data.description: This is a MUST SEE in the very SPECIAL and desirable neighborhood of Wildwood Place! Enter into this immaculate 3-bedroom 2-bath home through the double doors. Large windows bring natural light to the house and the open kitchen, dry bar area with built in wine rack, breakfast bar, walk-in pantry make it home! The covered patio and fully fenced backyard are great for outdoor get togethers. The neighborhood pool and park area are a MUST SEE and enjoyed by all.
